<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>426</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khi tiva ralchan ceu inn tha ah khin, Dawtnak in a kan zohmi sinah,
 Kannih vialte kan i tong kho lai maw? Kan i tonnak hnga zeitluk inn tha.

[C1]
   Hung cio u, (Hung cio u), hung cio u, (hung cio u), tiva ral a
   ceunak inn chungah, Hung cio u, (Hung cio u), hung cio u, (hung cio u) A
   zungzal a kan Dawtu sinah.

[V2]
 Zungzal ngaihchiat um lonak ram chungah, Kannih vialte kan i tong hnga
 maw? Zei bantuk i tonnak tha dah si lai, Khamh ciami hla kansa kho hnga
 maw?

[C2]
   Hung cio u, (Hung cio u), hung cio u, (hung cio u), tiva ral a
   ceunak inn chungah, Hung cio u, (Hung cio u), hung cio u, (hung cio u) A
   zungzal a kan Dawtu sinah.

[V3]
 A kan Khamhtu Bawi umnak khua chungah, Ton cionak kha a um te lai maw?
 A kan Dawtu bik kha kan hngal hnga maw? Zei bantuk tonnak tha a si lai.

[C3]
   Hung cio u, (Hung cio u), hung cio u, (hung cio u), tiva ral a
   ceunak inn chungah, Hung cio u, (Hung cio u), hung cio u, (hung cio u) A
   zungzal a kan Dawtu sinah.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<title>HUNG CIO U CH426</title>
</song>